Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定之日就在明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛藏在東部演習場的阿爾馮斯·愛力克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻被人造人普萊德和庫拉多尼所捕獲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:01:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾馮斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點 阿爾馮斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想走還太早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.82,0:02:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還得繼續…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我利用下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}黑暗的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問這裡是卡納馬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有客人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來了嗎 愛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算出氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然一拳打過來 真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是用右手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友增加了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是一起行動而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便一提 我是這些傢伙的老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兒子受你照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.95,0:03:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 還真是個夠狂妄的兒子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很特殊的刺青呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想隱瞞也沒用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔也別隱瞞 都說出來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就是約定之日吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 全都告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不能像阿爾馮斯那樣直率地接受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿爾也說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 雖然留有各種想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你非常想要的賢者之石就在這裡 要用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.89,0:04:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都是無辜者的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們因為自己的責任失去身體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了怎麼能安心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個能這麼說的兒子真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天會有日蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙打算利用那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用日蝕？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德華 能幫我阻止那傢伙的野心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫忙？別誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.92,0:05:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不和你聯手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會把那個鬍鬚男打飛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是現在和你聯手能獲得更高的勝率
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才聽你說話的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是以什麼理由 能夠和我一起戰鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比拿可婆婆托我傳給你媽媽的遺言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能遵守約定 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實傳達給你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和老爸多談一些不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對 至少叫他一聲老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然過去發生過不少事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他不是那種會丟下老婆的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有各種原因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好聽他講吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有各種原因
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種指什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正就是無聊的固執吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.18,0:06:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情沒理順吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒辦法 活人姿態的賢者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且居然是你老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是這些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 讓我有點意外
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總有一天也會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.07,0:07:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成滿臉皺紋的老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不論變成什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都想在一起開開心心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 一直做我們的家人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朵莉夏 我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.56,0:07:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能遵守約定 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.39,0:08:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒實現和妳一起逝世的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但始終相信著我之後一定會去妳那邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是明天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朵莉夏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿那個做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要穿那麼顯眼的衣服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計會成為最後的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須得鼓足精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 其實不需要跟著我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡分手對大叔們來說會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 手下不要擅作主張
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要恢復原來的身體什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個身體各方面都很方便
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實就這樣也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼別的可去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是在這裡會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是野生動物的直覺這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.91,0:09:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又是為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說要從人造人那裡溜走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想問我為什麼回到中央都市？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 別嚇我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和你會合真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還精神吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥也沒事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是去了邁爾斯少佐那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於這件事有話要談 來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾 你哪裡不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.69,0:10:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 有這麼個感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快離開那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到那邊了嗎 古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被那種人類控制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂太脆弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大總統還是去向不明？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.13,0:11:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在下游找到了一具部下的屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這如果活下來就是奇蹟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北方軍也協助我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來指揮搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.14,0:12:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中將親自出馬嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不親眼看到那傢伙的屍體就無法安心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不按照當初的目標 瞄準中央都市嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 中央都市就讓給馬斯坦古大佐了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現布拉德雷政權沒有發生什麼問題正常運轉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬斯坦古大佐和阿姆斯壯少將任何一方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果就這麼起事一定會被視為謀反
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果變成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時就是我出場的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.74,0:12:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那兩個人做惡人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後正義的伙伴古拉曼中將登場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓我以最小的風險 能得到這個國家的實權
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓年輕人去火中取栗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:12:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概就是這麼想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.14,0:13:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個老狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在約定之日的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是聯手了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但直到最後都不能放鬆警惕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿…阿爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是普萊德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普萊德？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們最大的長兄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.86,0:13:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要叛逆嗎 古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對我們來說已經只是個障礙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.41,0:13:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 為什麼知道了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 居然裝扮成阿爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是裝扮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這確實是你弟弟的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古利德就讓我在這裡處理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼之鍊金術師就和我一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 猩猩大叔們快逃…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 也太快了吧 你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們野生動物的直覺告訴我們不要和那個戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.12,0:14:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們因為需要我和阿爾所以無法殺我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻可以使出全力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.37,0:14:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不客氣地打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.03,0:14:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 不會殺你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有可能會折斷你兩三根手腳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.81,0:14:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能逃向貧民窟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防禦對這傢伙沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的朋友已經被我抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貧民窟的人也抓住的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.21,0:15:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會聽我的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下就刺中你最討厭的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總不能每次都讓你們佔上風
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停電
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也看不見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼球也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亨克爾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 因為有光才會有影子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全漆黑的話 他就無法實體化了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們一樣 什麼也看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是藏在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有燈光的話 又會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亨克爾 剛才看到阿爾馮斯的影子了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 像觸手一樣的東西彎彎曲曲的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會在大影子的旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本體在森林的影子中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本體？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎧甲不是本體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那傢伙專用的出門容器在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼樣的容器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮與星星都沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這黑暗之中對方也無法動彈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著貧民窟的燈光恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.15,0:17:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對著這個模樣毫不動搖地攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對小鬼動手心裡確實有點過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.26,0:17:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野性的直覺在狂叫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙不打倒就危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.27,0:18:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.13,0:18:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 愛德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.55,0:18:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猩猩先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你弟弟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有動的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要是動的話會喀嚓喀嚓響的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 暫時離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管阿爾了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你擔心他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果隨便接近他 中陷阱的話怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在亨克爾把普萊德搞定之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.51,0:18:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了避免自相殘殺必須待在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個聲音是獅子大叔在戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是黑暗就交給夜行動物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普萊德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼能知道我們的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙應該沒有這種能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:18:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼之鍊金術師的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古利德的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音是庫拉多尼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.64,0:19:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用庫拉多尼的嗅覺來找到我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.52,0:19:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有另一個沒見過的傢伙的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指名你呢 達律斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是人造人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼和那怪物級的傢伙戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是依靠氣味行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的話不是能對等戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明說野性的直覺還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好男人要有膽量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先手必殺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.01,0:20:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分 猩猩先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是為了避免自相殘殺才在一起的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在黑暗中因庫拉多尼的有利形勢而無法行動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要是點燈的話 普萊德就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩大了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 古利德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的話 能察覺到人造人的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到普萊德的也是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這黑暗中 還是我比較容易行動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別帶著這身體跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.88,0:20:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了 這本來就是我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.92,0:21:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你配合真太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.44,0:21:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生氣了 肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你們卻不快快讓我吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.90,0:21:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 整個都吞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.64,0:21:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是 那個時候的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等 你們在看什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我這個普通人說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖待著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有什麼在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.25,0:21:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個氣味…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.68,0:22:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等妳好久了 蘭芳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.49,0:24:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知己知彼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.71,0:24:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到的東西反而是恐懼的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.52,0:24:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夾著尾巴逃跑就是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.22,0:24:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果站穩腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.51,0:24:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絞盡腦汁戰鬥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.90,0:24:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能夠找到勝機
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.98,0:24:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.69,0:24:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.45,0:24:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第48話 地道的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.87,0:24:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以同伴的血為代價獲取勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.72,0:24:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是好還是壞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.84,0:00:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:24.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}無止境的旅途中  止步不前之時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:30.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}我們深深地歎氣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:38.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}再次放開了緊握的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:45.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}但是現在已經沒有什麼可怕的了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.45,0:00:53.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}連接心靈之間那堅固的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:59.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}決不會被斬斷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.25,0:01:08.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}繼續尋求 終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:14.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}在這個地方畫上句號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:24.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}悲傷與憤怒 化為力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.04,0:01:29.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}命運就在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.84,0:00:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.27,0:22:46.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}本是沒有交點的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:47.02,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天也
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.02,0:22:51.88,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}企圖奪走我們的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.50,0:22:57.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即使獲得了想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:22:58.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼卻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.45,0:23:03.43,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}無法坦率地會心一笑
